# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [1.31.6] - 2024-06-26

### Added

- Added JUnit and Mockito to project
- Added commentaries and JavaDoc
- Added unit tests for MovieController, ReviewController, UserController, MovieService, ReviewService and UserService
- Added integration test for MovieController

### Changed

- Changed gitlab-ci.yml file

### Removed

- Removed threads in MovieController and MovieService

## [1.30.6] - 2024-06-21

### Added

- Added method hasUserRatedMovie in ReviewService to find out if user already rated a movie and implemented method in calculateAverageRating

### Changed

- Changed createReview method -> rating is now optional
- Changed addFavorites method in UserService
- Changed date format of releaseDate in movie objects (movies.json)

### Fixed

- Fixed profile constructor 
- Fixed method to search by director

## [1.29.6] - 2024-06-21

### Changed

- Changed readme files and added seperate readme for project and backend

## [1.29.5] - 2024-06-19

### Added

- Added threads and parallel streams in classes MovieController and MovieService

## [1.28.5] - 2024-06-19

### Added

- Added CI/CD to project with new gitlab-ci.yml file

## [1.27.5] - 2024-06-17

### Fixed

- Fixed issue with logback xml file

## [1.27.4] - 2024-06-16

### Removed

- Removed wrong gitlab-ci.yml file 

## [1.27.3] - 2024-06-12

### Added

  [Frontend]

- Added logic to searchbar to find movies

## [1.26.3] - 2024-06-11

### Added

  [Backend]

- Added rating system to movie and review classes
- Added rated attribute to movies.json for age restriction information

### Changed
- Changed attribute "rating" in class Review from String to Integer
- Changed attribute "rating" in class Movie from String to Double

## [1.25.3] - 2024-06-10

### Added

  [Frontend]

- Added review endpoints and review services
- Added rating stars and rating view

