## [1.14.2] - 2024-05-14

### Added

  [Backend]

- Added delete endpoint for class user to delete user and profile from database
- Added two patch endpoints for class user to update email and password
- Added delete endpoint for class review to delete a review from database
- Added patch endpoint for class review to update an existing review
- Added code to create and delete review methods to count total amount of reviews

### Changed

  [Backend]

- Changed method getUserProfile and included user verification
- Changed methods findByUsername and findByEmail to ignoreCase

## [1.13.2] - 2024-05-13

