- Added home stylesheet

## [1.3.0] - 2024-04-26

### Added

  [Backend]

- Added architecture structure with packages for models, controllers, services and repositories
- Added endpoint for class UserController to get user profiles, add and remove movies to favorites

## [1.2.0] - 2024-04-21

### Added

  [Backend]

- Installed first backend portion
- Added java spring boot project
- Installed dependencies for spring boot starter-web, spring boot starter-mongodb, lombok
- Installed dotenv dependency for database login information
- Added classes for Movie, MovieController, MovieRepository and MovieService
- Added methods to get all or a single movie via REST
- Added classes for Review, ReviewController, ReviewRepository and ReviewService
- Added methods to create a review
- Added classes for User, UserController, UserRepository and UserService
- Added methods to create and authenticate users
- Added .env file and application.properties for database login information

## [1.1.0] - 2024-04-18

### Added

  [Frontend]

- Installed React-icons package
- Added responsive sidebar in frontend
- Added 'assets' directory for images and icons
- Added stylesheet for sidebar

## [1.0.0] - 2024-04-18

### Added

  [Frontend]

- Installed React for frontend development
- Installed routing library React-router-dom for web applications
- Created package architecture with pages and router directories
- Created 'Home' and 'Genres' pages